**PROPERTY ELIGIBLE FOR 100% FINANCING WITH NO PRIVATE MORTGAGE INSURANCE FOR FIRST TIME HOMEBUYERS THROUGH SOUTHSTATE BANK**

Welcome to 5924 Austin Woods! ! Built in 2022, this first floor owner suite townhome is perfect for you. Located near Chippenham Parkway, route 10, as well as a plethora of restaurants and shops. This home office a large great room and an open concept kitchen and dining area with an enormous center island; Perfect for entertaining! Up the stairs you will find two spacious bedrooms and you can find your owner suite with walk-in closet on the first floor. The community offers amenities such as a dog park, walking trails and fire pits. Come view this home today!
